Sorry!
Starting the game:
	Press 'Start'
	Select the number of players
	Select your color
Game Objective:
	Get all four of your pawns home
	Land on or slide over opponent pawns
Playing the game:
	Draw a card
	Select a square that is valid
	Select the square to move to
Special Cards:
	One/Two - Move out of start
	Two - Move 2 and draw again
	Four - Move backward 4
	Seven - Split move between 2 pawns
	Ten - Move back 1 or 10 forward
	Eleven - Swap positions or move 11 forward
	Sorry! - Swap positions from a pawn at start